' description: sdk-bridge 双端 (claude-code + codex-cli) 模块架构 — Codex live path uses app-server + mid-turn steering
' last_updated: 2026-06-10
@startuml sdk-bridge-architecture

title sdk-bridge — 双端模块架构 (Codex app-server + mid-turn steering)

' 内部 module 名 / 函数名 / LOC / commit / REVIEW 引用见 INDEX

package "Renderer / IPC steering surface" as L0 {
  [SessionDetail Composer\nsteer input] as SteerUI
  [preload steerAdapterTurn\n+ adapter:steer-turn IPC] as SteerIPC
}

package "公共抽象 (跨 adapter)" as L1 {
  [adapter 接口\n(两端共同实现)] as AdapterIf
  [会话管理器 + 4 张数据表 + 事件总线] as Common
}

package "claude-code 端" as L2 {
  [claude facade\n(创建 + 消息主路径)] as ClaudeFacade
  [claude 自愈层\n(recoverer + jsonl 兜底)] as ClaudeRec
  [stream-processor + restart-controller\n+ canUseTool 闭包] as ClaudeAux
}

package "codex-cli 端 (镜像)" as L3 {
  [codex facade\n(创建 + 消息主路径)] as CodexFacade
  [codex 自愈层\n(recoverer + jsonl 兜底)] as CodexRec
  [app-server client + thread-loop\n+ currentTurnId + translate\n+ rollback + resume-await + token-map] as CodexAux
}

package "SDK / protocol 子进程" as L4 {
  [claude SDK 子进程] as ClaudeSDK
  [codex app-server --stdio\n(JSON-RPC over stdio)] as CodexSDK
}

package "外部边界 (jsonl)" as L5 {
  folder "~/.claude/projects/<encoded-cwd>/<sid>.jsonl" as ClaudeJsonl
  folder "~/.codex/sessions/<YYYY>/<MM>/<DD>/rollout-<TS>-<thread_id>.jsonl\n(date-based, cwd-independent)" as CodexJsonl
}

' ─── 接口实现 ───

AdapterIf <|.. ClaudeFacade
AdapterIf <|.. CodexFacade
SteerUI --> SteerIPC : active turn input
SteerIPC --> AdapterIf : steerTurn(sessionId, text)

' ─── claude 端调用链 ───

ClaudeFacade --> ClaudeAux : helpers
ClaudeFacade --> ClaudeSDK : spawn 子进程 + 消息主路径
ClaudeFacade --> ClaudeRec : sendMessage 撞 absent → 自愈
ClaudeRec --> Common : 反查 cwd / 取消归档
ClaudeRec --> ClaudeJsonl : jsonl 文件兜底预检
ClaudeRec --> ClaudeFacade : 自愈完回主路径
ClaudeSDK --> ClaudeJsonl : 写 conversation history

' ─── codex 端调用链 (镜像 claude) ───

CodexFacade --> CodexAux : helpers
CodexFacade --> CodexSDK : app-server thread/start|resume\n+ turn/start 主路径
CodexFacade --> CodexAux : steerTurn guard\n(active currentTurnId)
CodexAux --> CodexSDK : turn/steer(expectedTurnId)\n(no turn override)
CodexFacade --> CodexRec : sendMessage 撞 absent → 自愈
CodexRec --> Common : 反查 cwd / 取消归档
CodexRec --> CodexJsonl : jsonl 文件兜底预检
CodexRec --> CodexFacade : 自愈完回主路径
CodexSDK --> CodexJsonl : 写 conversation history

' ─── 关键不变量 ───

note bottom of ClaudeFacade
  claude 端独有:
  - canUseTool 闭包 (lead 端权限审批回调)
  - in-process MCP transport
end note

note bottom of CodexFacade
  codex 端独有:
  - app-server --stdio 长连接 (JSON-RPC)
  - currentTurnId 来自 turn/started 通知,用于 turn/steer expectedTurnId
  - turn/steer 不产生 turn/started;review/compact turn 不可 steer
  - per-session token map (允许并发)
  - jsonl 兜底无 LLM 摘要 (精简版)
  - app-server notification translate + live token-rate
  - **jsonl 路径与 cwd 无关 (与 Claude `~/.claude/projects/<encoded-cwd>` 分叉)**:
    `~/.codex/sessions/<YYYY>/<MM>/<DD>/rollout-<TS>-<thread_id>.jsonl`
    实现 jsonl-discovery.ts:11-13,40-61 (±1 day 扫描 + 递归兜底, REVIEW_56 §F2)
end note

note bottom of Common
  双端 parity 维护成本驱动镜像 helper 抽出
  详细不变量见 sdk-bridge-state-machine 图
end note

@enduml
